duties_responsibilities.duty: Accurately load and unload trailers, verify route load(s), maintain shipping yard, and report overages and shortages.
Operate material handling equipment, troubleshoot issues with packing equipment, and participate in 'Cycle Counts'.
Count and check products for accuracy and quality, maintain accurate records, and operate pallet jack, forklift, etc.
Perform duties such as stacking/unstacking, carrying, standing, stooping, and lifting up to 50lbs.
Communicate effectively in English, work nights, weekends, and holidays, and be comfortable in a warm working environment.
